📘 About Quiz App
The Quiz App is an interactive desktop application designed to test knowledge across various categories. It allows users to attempt multiple-choice questions, view hints, and track scores. The project was developed as a mini-project to strengthen skills in application development, database handling, and coding practices.
✨ Features: • User-friendly Interface – Simple and intuitive design for smooth navigation. • Question Bank with Categories – Includes General Knowledge, History, Science, etc. • Hints System – Helpful hints for each question. • Scoring Mechanism – Automatic score calculation based on correct answers. • Login & Authentication – Secure login. • Database Integration – All questions, answers, and user details managed via SQL Server.
👨‍💻 Team Members & Roles: • Harshith Harish Poojary – Planning and Designing the application structure. • Vaishak U Shetty – Database Creation and Management. • Abhiram KR – Database integration, coding, data collection, and automation tools (ChatGPT & GitHub Copilot).
